casebody.data:
NEW JERSEY EDUCATION ASSOCIATION, et al., petitioners,
v.
NEW JERSEY, et al. No. 15-302. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 29, 2016.

Motion of New Jersey Public Employees' Retirement System, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of New Jersey denied.
